  sodium: 1730 mg
time required: 40 minutes
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/vegan-mushroom-white-bean-shepherds-pie-64ad6e6508c61453c499aad0
cuisine: Irish
course: main course
